   Bittersweet Pill
                                                                                                       

   One thing about the future
   Leaves me uninspired:
   What good is a vacation
   Once I have retired?
   -- Mimi Kay.
   ---
   Daffynition
                                                                                                       

   Drinking songs: gregarious chants.
   -- Rodney Stevens.
