<LP>
   OAKLAND, Calif. -- Equitec Financial Group Inc. said it
suspended quarterly interest payments on its secured line of
credit with PacifiCorp Credit Inc. The principal amount
outstanding under the line of credit is $10.1 million.
   PacifiCorp Credit is unit of PacifiCorp, a Portland, Ore.,
