<HL>
   Business Brief -- Durham Corp.:
   Group's $315 Million Offer
   Called `Highly Speculative'
</HL>
<DATE>
04/05/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
